{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b10m37c0-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
    "name": "Biometric API",
    "description": "Colección oficial del Biometric API (gestión de equipos biomédicos).\n\nIncluye:\n- Auth (JWT)\n- Users (CRUD + me + set_password) — fase 02.5\n- Branches (CRUD) — fase 02\n- Equipment (CRUD + by-asset-tag + regenerate-qr + history) — fase 03\n- Maintenance (CRUD historial + upload PDF) — fase 04\n\nCredencial de superusuario por defecto (creada manualmente):\n- username: admin\n- password: AdminPass123!\n\nFlujo recomendado: 1) `Auth › Login` para poblar `access_token`. 2) `Branches › Create` para poblar `branch_id`. 3) `Equipment › Create` para poblar `equipment_id`. 4) `Maintenance › Create` para poblar `maintenance_record_id`. 5) probar el resto.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",      "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token",  "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id",       "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "branch_id",     "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "equipment_id",  "value": "",                       "type": "string" },
    { "key": "asset_tag_sample", "value": "EQ-0001",             "type": "string" },
    { "key": "maintenance_record_id", "value": "",               "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (token obtain)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"AdminPass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token", ""]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve `access` y `refresh`. El test guarda ambos en variables de colección."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "const setAll = (key, value) => {",
                  "  if (!value) return;",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "  if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "  pm.globals.set(key, value);",
                  "};",
                  "setAll('access_token', body.access);",
                  "setAll('refresh_token', body.refresh);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token", "refresh", ""]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.access) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access);",
                  "  if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) pm.environment.set('access_token', body.access);",
                  "  pm.globals.set('access_token', body.access);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify token",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{access_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token/verify/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token", "verify", ""]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
